code: @Override public void setClusterInformation(C clusterId, String webInterfaceUrl) {     if (this.clusterId != null || this.webInterfaceUrl != null) {         throw new IllegalStateException("Cluster information is already present.").     }     this.clusterId = clusterId.     this.webInterfaceUrl = webInterfaceUrl. }
public C getClusterId() {     if (this.clusterId == null) {         throw new IllegalStateException("Cluster ID has not been set.").     }     return clusterId. }

public String getWebInterfaceUrl() {     if (this.webInterfaceUrl == null) {         throw new IllegalStateException("Cluster web interface URL has not been set.").     }     return webInterfaceUrl. }
